\c 18
\s UElija uthuma uObhadiya kuAhabi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi \add emva\add* kwensuku ezinengi ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kuElija ngomnyaka wesithathu lisithi: Hamba, uziveze kuAhabi\x + 17.1. Luka 4.25.\x*, sengizanisa izulu ebusweni bomhlaba\x + Dute. 28.12.\x*.
\v 2 UElija wasesiya ukuziveza kuAhabi. Njalo indlala yayilamandla eSamariya.
\v 3 UAhabi wasebiza uObhadiya owayephezu kwendlu \add yakhe\add*. UObhadiya wayeyesaba-ke kakhulu iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 4 Ngoba kwathi lapho uJezebeli ebhubhisa\f + \fk ebhubhisa: \fl Heb. \fq equma.\f* abaprofethi beN\nd kosi\nd*, uObhadiya wathatha abaprofethi abalikhulu, wabafihla ngamadoda angamatshumi amahlanu ebhalwini, wabondla ngesinkwa langamanzi.
\v 5 UAhabi wasesithi kuObhadiya: Hamba elizweni uye emithonjeni yonke yamanzi lezifuleni zonke; mhlawumbe singathola utshani, silondoloze amabhiza lezimbongolo kuphila, ukuze singabhubhisi okwezifuyo.
\v 6 Basebesehlukaniselana ilizwe ukuthi badabule phakathi kwalo; uAhabi wahamba ngenye indlela yedwa, uObhadiya laye wahamba ngenye indlela yedwa.
\p
\v 7 Kwasekusithi uObhadiya esendleleni, khangela-ke, uElija wamhlangabeza; wamnanzelela, wawa ngobuso bakhe wathi: Nguwe yini, nkosi yami, Elija?
\v 8 Wasesithi kuye: Yimi. Hamba u\add ye\add*tshela inkosi yakho \add ukuthi\add*: Khangela, uElija \add ulapha\add*.
\v 9 Wasesithi: Ngoneni ukuthi unikele inceku yakho esandleni sikaAhabi ukuthi angibulale?
\v 10 Kuphila kukaJehova uNkulunkulu wakho, kakulasizwe lombuso inkosi yami engathumelanga kukho ukukudinga. Lapho besithi: Kakho; yafungisa lowombuso lalesosizwe ukuthi kabakutholanga.
\v 11 Khathesi-ke uthi: Hamba utshele inkosi yakho \add ukuthi\add*: Khangela, uElija \add ulapha\add*.
\v 12 Kuzakuthi-ke sengisukile kuwe, uMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* akuthwale akuse lapho engingazi khona\x + 2 Kho. 2.16. Hez. 3.12,14. 8.3. Seb. 8.39.\x*; lapho sengifike ngatshela uAhabi, angakutholi, uzangibulala; kodwa \add mina\add* inceku yakho ngiyayesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* kusukela ebutsheni bami.
\v 13 Kakutshelwanga inkosi yami yini engakwenzayo lapho uJezebeli ebulala abaprofethi beN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuthi ngafihla amadoda alikhulu kubaprofethi beN\nd kosi\nd*, ngamadoda angamatshumi amahlanu ebhalwini, ngabondla ngesinkwa langamanzi?
\v 14 Khathesi-ke uthi: Hamba u\add ye\add*tshela inkosi yakho \add ukuthi\add*: Khangela uElija \add ulapha\add*. Abesengibulala.
\v 15 UElija wasesithi: Kuphila kukaJehova wamabandla engimi phambi kwakhe\x + 17.1.\x*, oqotho lamuhla ngizaziveza kuye.
\v 16 Ngakho uObhadiya wahamba ukuhlangabeza uAhabi, wamtshela; loAhabi wayahlangabeza uElija.
\p
\v 17 Kwasekusithi uAhabi ebona uElija, uAhabi wathi kuye: Nguwe yini\x + 21.20.\x* ongumhluphi kaIsrayeli\x + Josh. 6.18. Seb. 16.20.\x*?
\v 18 Wasesithi: Kangimhluphanga uIsrayeli, kodwa nguwe lendlu kayihlo\x + Josh. 6.18. Seb. 16.20.\x*, ngokuyitshiya kwenu imilayo yeN\nd kosi\x + 2 Lan. 15.2.\x*\nd*, lalandela oBhali\x + 16.31.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho-ke thuma, ubuthanisele kimi uIsrayeli wonke entabeni iKharmeli\x + Josh. 19.26.\x*, labaprofethi bakaBhali abangamakhulu amane lamatshumi amahlanu labaprofethi bezixuku abangamakhulu amane\x + 16.33.\x* abadla etafuleni likaJezebeli\x + 2 Kho. 3.13.\x*.
\v 20 Ngakho uAhabi wathuma phakathi kwabo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli, wabuthanisa abaprofethi\x + 22.6.\x* entabeni iKharmeli\x + Josh. 19.26.\x*.
\s UElija labaprofethi bakaBhali eKharmeli
\p
\v 21 UElija wasesondela ebantwini bonke wathi: Koze kube nini liqhula emicabangweni emibili? Uba iN\nd kosi\nd* inguNkulunkulu, landelani yona\x + Josh. 24.15. 2 Kho. 17.41.\x*; kodwa uba kunguBhali, mlandeleni. Kodwa abantu kabamphendulanga \add nga\add*lizwi.
\v 22 UElija wasesithi ebantwini: Mina ngedwa ngingumprofethi weN\nd kosi\nd* oseleyo\x + 19.10,14.\x*; kodwa abaprofethi bakaBhali ngamadoda angamakhulu amane lamatshumi amahlanu\x + 18.19.\x*.
\v 23 Ngakho kabasinike amajongosi amabili, bazikhethele ijongosi elilodwa, baliqume iziqa, bazibeke phezu kwenkuni, bangafaki mlilo; lami ngizalungisa elinye ijongosi, ngilibeke phezu kwenkuni, ngingafaki mlilo.
\v 24 Njalo bizani ibizo likankulunkulu wenu, lami ngizabiza ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd*; uNkulunkulu ozaphendula ngomlilo nguye uNkulunkulu\x + 18.38.\x*. Bonke abantu basebephendula bathi: Lelilizwi lilungile.
\p
\v 25 UElija wasesithi kubaprofethi bakaBhali: Zikhetheleni ijongosi elilodwa, lililungise kuqala, ngoba libanengi, libize ibizo likankulunkulu wenu, kodwa lingafaki mlilo.
\v 26 Basebethatha ijongosi ababelinikiwe, balilungisa, babiza ibizo likaBhali kusukela ekuseni kwaze kwaba semini, besithi: Bhali, siphendule! Kodwa kakubanga lalizwi, kakubanga lophendulayo. Basebeseqa phezu kwelathi elalenziwe.
\v 27 Kwasekusithi emini uElija wadlala ngabo wathi: Memezani ngelizwi elikhulu, ngoba ungunkulunkulu; ngoba uyanakana, loba umonyukile, kumbe usekuhambeni, mhlawumbe ulele, njalo kudingeka ukuthi avuswe.
\v 28 Basebememeza ngelizwi elikhulu, bazisika njengokomkhuba wabo ngezinkemba langemikhonto, kwaze kwantshaza igazi kubo\x + Levi 19.28. Dute. 14.1.\x*.
\v 29 Kwasekusithi sekwedlulile imini, baprofetha kwaze kwaba sekunikelweni komnikelo\x + 18.36. Eks. 29.41. Seb. 3.1. 2 Kho. 3.20.\x*, kakubanga lelizwi, njalo kakubanga lophendulayo, njalo kakubanga lonakekelayo\x + 18.26.\x*.
\p
\v 30 UElija wasesithi ebantwini bonke: Sondelani kimi. Bonke abantu basebesondela kuye. Waselungisa ilathi leN\nd kosi\nd* elaselidilikile\x + 19.10,14.\x*.
\v 31 UElija wasethatha amatshe alitshumi lambili, ngokwenani lezizwe zamadodana kaJakobe, okwafika kuye ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lisithi: Ibizo lakho lizakuba nguIsrayeli\x + Gen. 32.28.\x*.
\v 32 Ngalawomatshe wasesakha ilathi ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd*, wenza umgelo ozingelezela ilathi, ngokwesilinganiso \w samaseya\w** amabili enhlanyelo.
\v 33 Waselungisa inkuni, waliquma iziqa ijongosi, wa\add li\add*beka phezu kwenkuni\x + Levi 1.7.\x*, wasesithi: Gcwalisani izimbiza ezine ngamanzi, liwathele phezu komnikelo wokutshiswa laphezu kwenkuni\x + Hlu. 6.20.\x*.
\v 34 Wasesithi: Kwenzeni okwesibili. Bakwenza okwesibili. Wathi: Kwenzeni okwesithathu. Basebekwenza okwesithathu.
\v 35 Amanzi asehamba azingelezela ilathi, lomgelo lawo wawugcwalisa ngamanzi\x + 18.32,38.\x*.
\p
\v 36 Kwasekusithi ekunikelweni komnikelo uElija umprofethi wasondela wathi: N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu kaAbrahama, uIsaka, loIsrayeli\x + Eks. 3.6.\x*, kakwaziwe lamuhla ukuthi unguNkulunkulu koIsrayeli\x + 20.13. Josh. 4.24. 1 Sam. 17.46.\x*, lami ngiyinceku yakho, lokuthi ngizenzile zonke lezizinto njengokwelizwi lakho\x + Nani 16.28.\x*.
\v 37 Ngiphendule, N\nd kosi\nd*, ungiphendule, ukuze lababantu bazi ukuthi wena uyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu, lokuthi uyiphendulile futhi inhliziyo yabo.
\v 38 Wasusehla umlilo weN\nd kosi\nd*, waqothula umnikelo wokutshiswa lenkuni lamatshe lothuli, wakhotha lamanzi asemgelweni\x + Levi 9.24. 1 Lan. 21.26.\x*.
\v 39 Kwathi abantu bonke bekubona bathi mbo ngobuso babo, bathi: UJehova nguye onguNkulunkulu; uJehova nguye onguNkulunkulu\x + 18.24.\x*.
\v 40 UElija wasesithi kibo: Babambeni abaprofethi bakaBhali, kungaphunyuki lamunye wabo. Basebebabamba. UElija wasebehlisela esifuleni iKishoni\x + Hlu. 4.7.\x*, wababulalela khona\x + Dute. 13.1-5. 18.20. 2 Kho. 10.25.\x*.
\s Ukuphela kwendlala
\p
\v 41 UElija wasesithi kuAhabi: Yenyuka, udle unathe, ngoba kulomsindo wobunengi bezulu.
\v 42 UAhabi wasesenyuka ukuyakudla lokunatha. UElija wasesenyukela engqongeni yeKharmeli\x + Josh. 19.26.\x*; wakhothamela phansi emhlabathini, wafaka ubuso bakhe phakathi kwamadolo akhe\x + 2 Kho. 4.34,35. Jak. 5.18.\x*.
\v 43 Wasesithi encekwini yakhe: Yenyuka khathesi, ukhangele ngaselwandle. Yasisenyuka, yakhangela, yathi: Kakulalutho. Wasesithi: Buyela, kasikhombisa.
\v 44 Kwasekusithi ngesikhathi sesikhombisa yathi: Khangela, iyezana elingangesandla somuntu lisenyuka olwandle\x + Luka 12.54.\x*. Wasesithi: Yenyuka uyetshela uAhabi: Bophela \add inqola\add*, wehle, hlezi izulu likuvalele\x + Gen. 46.29. Eks. 14.6. 2 Kho. 9.21. Jer. 46.4.\x*.
\v 45 Kwasekusithi kungakafiki lesosikhathi isibhakabhaka sasesisiba mnyama ngamayezi langomoya, kwaba lezulu elikhulu. UAhabi wasegada, waya eJizereyeli\x + Josh. 17.16.\x*.
\v 46 Lesandla seN\nd kosi\nd* sasiphezu kukaElija\x + 2 Kho. 3.15.\x*; wabopha ukhalo lwakhe, wagijima phambi kukaAhabi\x + 2 Kho. 4.29. 9.1. Jobe 38.3. 40.7. Isa. 11.5. Jer. 1.17. Luka 12.35. Efe. 6.14. 1 Pet. 1.13. Eks. 12.11.\x*, uze ufike eJizereyeli\x + Josh. 17.16.\x*.
